    <item>
      <title>英特尔获得美国 200 亿美元赠款和贷款用于芯片工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/intel-wins-almost-20-billion-in-chips-incentives-for-us-plants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国将向英特尔公司提供 85 亿美元的赠款和高达 110 亿美元的贷款，以资助其半导体工厂的扩建，这是旨在重振国内芯片行业的计划中获得的最大一笔资助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/intel-wins-almost-20-billion-in-chips-incentives-for-us-plants</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>销售额未达预期，腾讯回购额翻倍至超过 128 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/tencent-sales-disappoint-after-pervasive-chinese-slowdown-bites</link>
      <description><![CDATA[腾讯控股有限公司计划到 2024 年将其股票回购计划增加一倍以上，达到至少 128 亿美元，以安抚投资者对中国经济低迷期间增长逐渐消退的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/tencent-sales-disappoint-after-pervasive-chinese-slowdown-bites</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 08:47:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谷歌在法国与新闻媒体的冲突中被罚款 2.5 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/google-fined-250-million-in-french-clash-with-news-publishers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alphabet Inc.旗下的谷歌被法国竞争监管机构罚款2.5亿欧元（合2.71亿美元），原因是其未能履行承诺，与媒体机构达成公平协议，发布其内容链接，包括掠夺新闻文章来训练其人工智能技术，而不通知他们。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/google-fined-250-million-in-french-clash-with-news-publishers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 08:10:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
